I spoke to KSL. He's having some probs getting online, but he'll be back and get the IGL going as soon as he can.

::Prowl/Rixer::

Prowl watches calmly as five bots materialize around him in the holo-room, three of them instantly jumping at him. He jumps up, activating his jets and clearing out of the way, watching them smash into each other under him.

"Come on, Cyndro, you can do better than that!" Prowl says, turning and seeing that there were only four bots bots under him now.

"Oof!" He feels the fifth bot slam into his back from behind, sending him flying forward and into the other four, one of them slamming a fist into his stomach, another a fist into his back.

-Slag,- Prowl thinks as he drops to the ground, instantly sweeping a foot out and tripping two of his enemies, then jumping up with a kick to a third one's head. -How in the pit to I transform into that SMB??!-

He lands on the ground, instantly crouching and sweeping his foot out behind him, tripping the two bots that were just getting up.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Rixer steps out of the CR chamber, stretching to make sure all his joints were working fine. He sets off in no particular direction, wandering aimlessly.
